              <span id="reviewTextContainer3874477090" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer12205138607226792124">I read the first three books years ago and loved them with a passion. I adore fairy tales, and what Funke does with her world behind the mirrors is unique and masterful. <br/>This fourth one came out recently, and it took me a while to get into it. I started out reading the print edition, and then switched to the audio version, which worked better for me. The German audio book is excellent, with very fitting music adding to the magical feel of the story. Sadly I had technical issues with the Onleihe </span>
  <span id="freeText12205138607226792124" style="display:none">I read the first three books years ago and loved them with a passion. I adore fairy tales, and what Funke does with her world behind the mirrors is unique and masterful. <br />This fourth one came out recently, and it took me a while to get into it. I started out reading the print edition, and then switched to the audio version, which worked better for me. The German audio book is excellent, with very fitting music adding to the magical feel of the story. Sadly I had technical issues with the Onleihe app, which was super annoying. Even worse: there is an open ending which resolves nothing. Grrrr...</span>
