        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer3667730933" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer8151523242384360213">Cornelia Funke is still a masterful storyteller. <br/><br/>Some major cliffhangers. Hope the next book comes out soon.<br/><br/>What happened to Spieler?<br/>Will the fairies come back?<br/>What about the love triangle?<br/>And the creatures on Hideo’s skin?</span>

          </span>
